ses its tail straight up. It is a signal that it is about to pounce and bite."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Although its fur has many admirers, it is tough to raise as a pet because of its fickle meanness."},{"version":"diamond","text":"A very haughty Pok\u00e9mon. Among fans, the size of the jewel in its forehead is a topic of much talk."},{"version":"pearl","text":"A very haughty Pok\u00e9mon. Among fans, the size of the jewel in its forehead is a topic of much talk."},{"version":"platinum","text":"A very haughty Pok\u00e9mon. Among fans, the size of the jewel in its forehead is a topic of much talk."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Many adore it for its sophisticated air. However, it will lash out and scratch for little reason."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Its lithe muscles allow it to walk without making a sound. It attacks in an instant."},{"version":"black","text":"A very haughty Pok\u00e9mon. Among fans, the size of the jewel in its forehead is a topic of much talk."},{"version":"white","text":"A very haughty Pok\u00e9mon. Among fans, the size of the jewel in its forehead is a topic of much talk."},{"version":"black-2","text":"A very haughty Pok\u00e9mon. Among fans, the size of the jewel in its forehead is a topic of much talk."},{"version":"white-2","text":"A very haughty Pok\u00e9mon. Among fans, the size of the jewel in its forehead is a topic of much talk."},{"version":"x","text":"Although its fur has many admirers, it is tough to raise as a pet because of its fickle meanness."},{"version":"y","text":"Its lithe muscles allow it to walk without making a sound. It attacks in an instant."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Persian has six bold whiskers that give it a look of toughness. The whiskers sense air movements to determine what is in the Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s surrounding vicinity. It becomes docile if grabbed by the whiskers."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Persian has six bold whiskers that give it a look of toughness. The whiskers sense air movements to determine what is in the Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s surrounding vicinity. It becomes docile if grabbed by the whiskers."},{"version":"sun","text":"It has a violent temperament. It will attack anything that looks it in the eye. Its sharp claws inflict deep wounds."},{"version":"moon","text":"It has a high opinion of itself, although not to the same extent as the Alolan Persian. It\u2019s quite difficult to make friends with this Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Although the jewel on its forehead appears to be a different color than those of Alolan Persian, it\u2019s mostly made of the same material."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon is popular with rich people. It\u2019s also targeted by hunters who are after the jewel in its forehead."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"The gem in its forehead glows on its own! It walks with all the grace and elegance of a proud queen."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"The gem in its forehead glows on its own! It walks with all the grace and elegance of a proud queen."},{"version":"sword","text":"Getting this prideful Pok\u00e9mon to warm up to you takes a lot of effort, and it will claw at you the moment it gets annoyed."},{"version":"shield","text":"Its elegant and refined behavior clashes with that of the barbaric Perrserker. The relationship between the two is one of mutual disdain."}],"evo":{"name":"meowth","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"persian","level":1,"min_level":28,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]},{"name":"pe